<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Pick your favorite <strong>surviving&nbsp;</strong>character.</li>



<li>Write down <em>Legendary </em><strong><em>PROFESSION/OCCUPATION</em></strong><em> Survivor of </em><strong><em>0 Level Adventure</em></strong> as your background.</li>



<li>Gain proficiency in your profession weapon, tools and anything related to your profession.</li>



<li>Pick adventuring class!</li>



<li>Add max result possible on class hit die to current hit dice.</li>



<li>Convert &#8220;Personality&#8221; into charisma or wisdom.</li>



<li>Duplicate third highest ability score, and put into missing ability score(One not chosen in step 8).</li>



<li>Spend 1 point of luck to increase another <br>ability score by one to a maximum of <em>18 + racial modifier</em> for that <br>ability score. <br>Example: A Dragonborn has a max strength of +2 for total MAX of 20.<strong> <br>DO NOT add racial adjustments into ability scores, racial modifiers only increase ability score maximums at this stage under this system.</strong></li>



<li>Add all the ability scores, and subtract 66. If this number is positive add this to your luck and repeat the previous step.</li>



<li>Mark down any class abilities you got at level one as per normal 5e Character Creation</li>
</ol>
